Duncan et al. v. Bluthenthal et al. April 15, 1895. By two Justices.

Brought forward from the last term.

Petition for injunction. Before Judge Janes. Haralson county. August 3, 1894. John A. Wimpy, for plaintiffs. J. M. McBride and Edwards & Edwards, for defendants. Simmons, C. J.

Under the facts appearing in the record, there was; no error in denying the injunction prayed for. Judgment affirmed.
